# Demo for `kit lineup` (table + tree).
# Render with: vhs vhs/lineup.tape  → produces vhs/lineup.gif

Output vhs/lineup.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "kit lineup"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "kit lineup --tree"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
